OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBreezy start with a mixture of
OL,6,Fsunny spells and showers, occasionally
OL,7,Fheavy. Winds will ease through the
OL,8,Fday, with showers also fading into the
OL,9,Fevening. Temperatures cooler than on
OL,10,FWednesday.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMainly dry with some evening
OL,13,Fsunshine, then cloud thickens from the
OL,14,Fwest, bringing late-evening rain,
OL,15,Fheavy at times. Winds strengthen later.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FBreezy. Rain initially light,
OL,18,Fturning heavier mid-morning before
OL,19,Fclearing east. Isolated afternoon
OL,20,Fshowers possible, with brighter or
OL,21,Fsunny spells developing by evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
